				<a href="/author/claire-lower/" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Claire Lower</span></a>
				<time datetime="2020-02-01T07:30:00+11:00" itemprop="datePublished">01 Feb 2020 7:30 AM</time>
			</div>
			<div class="trending-river__excerpt" itemprop="description">
				Scrambled eggs are easy to make, but they're kind of difficult to make perfectly. Rubbery, dry curds are no good, but runny scrambles can be just as offensive. Don't worry though, we're going to show you how to make perfect scrambled eggs every time, no matter how you like 'em.			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="trending-river__post" id="trending-post-2">
		<div class="trending-river__thumbnail col-sm-4">

				<a href="https://www.lifehacker.com.au/2020/02/how-to-watch-the-2020-super-bowl-live-in-australia" title="Read more">
					<img data-src="https://edge.alluremedia.com.au/m/l/2018/02/170205184112-03-super-bowl-51-super-169-410x231.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="49ers au chiefs feature gridiron nfl super-bowl">
				</a>
		</div>
		<div class="trending-river__content col-sm-8">
			<h2 class="trending-river__headline" itemprop="headline">
				<a href="https://www.lifehacker.com.au/2020/02/how-to-watch-the-2020-super-bowl-live-in-australia" title="Read more">
					Super Bowl 2020: How To Watch Live, Online And Free				</a>
			</h2>
			<div class="trending-river__meta">
				<a href="/author/sarah-basford/" rel="author"><span itemprop="author">Sarah Basford</span></a>
				<time datetime="2020-02-01T11:15:15+11:00" itemprop="datePublished">01 Feb 2020 11:15 AM</time>
			</div>
			<div class="trending-river__excerpt" itemprop="description">
				It's nearly February, which means it's Super Bowl season. This year will see the San Francisco 49ers take on the Kansas City Chiefs in Florida and despite being at least 14,000 kilometres away, Australians can watch it all live.			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

